The hon. Member for Twickenham (Munira Wilson) cited the partnership that Reach Academy Feltham has with two prominent local private schools. That is, of course, one of 7,000 such partnerships with 936 primary schools.[Official Report, 19 January 2023, Vol. 726, c. 10MC.]
The Government are committed to raising standards in our schools, and we have succeeded in raising standards in our schools, although there is more to do.
